## Credential Management

Users can generate and manage API credentials through the Amplitude web application. The platform emphasizes security best practices, including:
- Keeping secret keys private
- Using appropriate keys for client-side vs. server-side implementations
- Managing access control through proper credential usage
- Potentially rotating keys for enhanced security

API credentials can be found in the web application under Settings > Projects > General tab, where both API keys and Secret keys are accessible for authorized users.